2
00:00:09,808 --> 00:00:11,607
<font color=#FFFF00><i>(Episode 39)</i></font>

3
00:00:38,210 --> 00:00:39,280
<font color=#FFFF00>Kenapa?</font>

4
00:00:39,411 --> 00:00:41,280
<font color=#FFFF00>Kakimu terluka lagi? Kau bilang
sudah membaik.</font>

5
00:00:41,451 --> 00:00:43,021
<font color=#FFFF00>Ini bukan seperti itu.</font>

6
00:00:43,320 --> 00:00:45,421
<font color=#FFFF00>Pergelangan kakiku terkilir
saat aku turun dari mobil.</font>

7
00:00:45,650 --> 00:00:47,661
<font color=#FFFF00>Coba aku periksa.
/ Aku baik-baik saja.</font>

8
00:00:50,061 --> 00:00:51,231
<font color=#FFFF00>Kubilang aku baik-baik saja.</font>

9
00:00:55,761 --> 00:00:58,030
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau sungguh baik-baik saja?
Kau masih mampu melakukan operasi?</font>

10
00:00:58,131 --> 00:01:00,470
<font color=#FFFF00>Bagaimana jika aku tidak bisa?
Bisakah kau melakukannya untukku?</font>

11
00:01:01,441 --> 00:01:02,841
<font color=#FFFF00>Astaga.</font>

12
00:01:03,470 --> 00:01:06,671
<font color=#FFFF00>Jangan khawatir.
Ini hanya agak sakit.</font>

13
00:01:17,690 --> 00:01:18,720
<font color=#FFFF00>Pisau bedah.</font>

14
00:01:23,561 --> 00:01:25,461
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Irrigation. Suction.</i></font>

15
00:01:25,461 --> 00:01:27,360
<font color=#FFFF00><i>(Suction: Menyedot campuran gas
atau cairan)</i></font>

16
00:01:29,561 --> 00:01:30,571
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Retractor.</i></font>

17
00:01:30,571 --> 00:01:32,401
<font color=#FFFF00><i>(Retractor: Alat yang digunakan
untuk memperlebar sayatan)</i></font>

18
00:02:04,571 --> 00:02:06,571
<font color=#FFFF00>Bagaimana hasilnya?</font>

19
00:02:06,571 --> 00:02:07,970
<font color=#FFFF00>Operasinya berjalan lancar.</font>

20
00:02:08,971 --> 00:02:11,270
<font color=#FFFF00>Saat ini pasien sudah stabil, jadi
Anda dapat segera memindahkan dia.</font>

21
00:02:11,270 --> 00:02:12,411
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya, baiklah.</font>

22
00:02:13,011 --> 00:02:15,740
<font color=#FFFF00>Terima kasih.
/ Silakan masuk.</font>

23
00:02:37,231 --> 00:02:38,971
<font color=#FFFF00>Silakan kopinya.</font>

24
00:02:40,541 --> 00:02:42,971
<font color=#FFFF00>Kenapa? Kakimu masih sakit?</font>

25
00:02:43,610 --> 00:02:44,770
<font color=#FFFF00>Agak.</font>

26
00:02:46,011 --> 00:02:48,911
<font color=#FFFF00>Mintalah Dr Kim untuk akupunktur.
Dia bilang itu efektif.</font>

27
00:02:50,710 --> 00:02:52,180
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau tidak mau?</font>

28
00:02:53,150 --> 00:02:55,751
<font color=#FFFF00>Bisakah kau membawakanku koyo?</font>

29
00:02:56,451 --> 00:02:59,791
<font color=#FFFF00>Bagaimana jika di rontgen dahulu?</font>

30
00:02:59,951 --> 00:03:02,761
<font color=#FFFF00>Lututmu terlihat agak bengkak.</font>

31
00:03:03,490 --> 00:03:05,261
<font color=#FFFF00>Kurasa tidak.</font>

32
00:03:06,060 --> 00:03:08,860
<font color=#FFFF00>Lakukan rontgen. Bagaimana jika
ada retakan tipis?</font>

33
00:03:08,930 --> 00:03:11,400
<font color=#FFFF00>Bagaimana jika itu semakin memburuk
dan kau memerlukan gips?</font>

34
00:03:11,671 --> 00:03:13,640
<font color=#FFFF00>Siapa yang akan mengoperasi
pasien kita?</font>

35
00:03:15,671 --> 00:03:17,110
<font color=#FFFF00>Kalau begitu, haruskah?</font>

36
00:03:19,110 --> 00:03:21,210
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau begitu mencintai operasi.</font>

37
00:03:21,441 --> 00:03:24,150
<font color=#FFFF00>Mendengar kata operasi saja,
kau segera berubah...</font>

38
00:03:24,310 --> 00:03:25,481
<font color=#FFFF00>Perawat Yoo.</font>

39
00:03:26,810 --> 00:03:28,481
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau perlu bantuan?
/ Tidak.</font>

40
00:03:29,150 --> 00:03:30,150
<font color=#FFFF00>Haruskah aku...</font>

41
00:03:30,990 --> 00:03:32,791
<font color=#FFFF00>...meminta bantuan dokter Kwak?</font>

42
00:03:33,960 --> 00:03:35,921
<font color=#FFFF00>Kenapa kau ingin melakukan itu?</font>

43
00:03:37,661 --> 00:03:40,161
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku juga penasaran.
Kenapa aku melakukan itu ya?</font>

44
00:03:45,770 --> 00:03:46,800
<font color=#FFFF00>Dokter.</font>

45
00:03:48,441 --> 00:03:49,441
<font color=#FFFF00>Retakan tipis?</font>

46
00:03:50,101 --> 00:03:53,680
<font color=#FFFF00>Bentuknya pasti lebih buruk
jika itu terjadi.</font>

47
00:03:53,680 --> 00:03:55,610
<font color=#FFFF00>Kakimu pasti sudah sanagt bengkak.</font>

48
00:03:55,781 --> 00:03:56,810
<font color=#FFFF00>Benarkah?</font>

49
00:03:57,481 --> 00:03:59,580
<font color=#FFFF00>Kalau begitu, lupakan saja.
/ Tunggu.</font>

50
00:04:00,381 --> 00:04:02,381
<font color=#FFFF00>Mari kita lakukan saja.</font>

51
00:04:02,481 --> 00:04:04,691
<font color=#FFFF00>Lebih baik aman daripada menyesal.</font>

52
00:04:05,221 --> 00:04:06,351
<font color=#FFFF00>Berbaringlah.</font>

53
00:04:09,421 --> 00:04:10,890
<font color=#FFFF00>Mari kita lihat.</font>

54
00:04:16,430 --> 00:04:18,831
<font color=#FFFF00>Jangan bergerak.</font>

55
00:04:20,940 --> 00:04:21,940
<font color=#FFFF00><i>(Ruang rontgen)</i></font>

56
00:04:30,750 --> 00:04:31,981
<font color=#FFFF00>Jangan lakukan ini.</font>

57
00:04:31,981 --> 00:04:34,320
<font color=#FFFF00>Perawat Yoo sepertinya tahu
tentang kita.</font>

58
00:04:34,320 --> 00:04:35,680
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia kenapa?</font>

59
00:04:36,421 --> 00:04:37,450
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia bilang apa?</font>

60
00:04:37,450 --> 00:04:39,351
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau tidak boleh melanggar aturan
yang pertama.</font>

61
00:04:40,050 --> 00:04:41,820
<font color=#FFFF00>Aturan pertama yang mana ya?</font>

62
00:04:41,820 --> 00:04:44,391
<font color=#FFFF00>"Jangan pegang pergelangan tanganku
di kapal rumah sakit."</font>

63
00:04:46,690 --> 00:04:48,800
<font color=#FFFF00>Kalau begitu, bolehkah aku memegang
pergelangan kakimu? / Apa?</font>

64
00:04:54,641 --> 00:04:57,070
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku yang akan melakukannya.
/ Diamlah.</font>

65
00:05:20,300 --> 00:05:21,860
<font color=#FFFF00>Mari kita lihat.</font>

66
00:05:21,860 --> 00:05:25,930
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa tulang Dokter Song retak
atau tidak?</font>

67
00:05:28,841 --> 00:05:29,870
<font color=#FFFF00>Tunggu.</font>

68
00:05:32,041 --> 00:05:33,110
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa ini?</font>

69
00:05:40,010 --> 00:05:41,081
<font color=#FFFF00>Ini...</font>

70
00:05:46,391 --> 00:05:47,820
<font color=#FFFF00>Sudah ada hasilnya?</font>

71
00:05:48,820 --> 00:05:50,190
<font color=#FFFF00>Tolong kirimkan padaku.</font>

72
00:05:51,130 --> 00:05:52,161
<font color=#FFFF00>Dokter Song.</font>

73
00:05:53,930 --> 00:05:55,430
<font color=#FFFF00>Kemari dan duduklah.</font>

74
00:05:56,300 --> 00:05:58,531
<font color=#FFFF00>Kenapa? Apa itu parah?</font>

75
00:05:58,901 --> 00:06:00,031
<font color=#FFFF00>Duduklah.</font>

76
00:06:18,950 --> 00:06:20,021
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa ini...</font>

77
00:06:22,421 --> 00:06:23,490
<font color=#FFFF00>...punyaku?</font>

78
00:06:28,901 --> 00:06:30,031
<font color=#FFFF00>Ini punyaku?</font>

79
00:06:32,800 --> 00:06:35,200
<font color=#FFFF00>Mari kita lakukan rontgen lagi.</font>

80
00:06:50,690 --> 00:06:52,151
<font color=#FFFF00>Selesai.</font>

81
00:06:59,190 --> 00:07:02,130
<font color=#FFFF00>Ikat yang benar dan erat.
Nanti terangkat oleh angin.</font>

82
00:07:02,130 --> 00:07:03,130
<font color=#FFFF00>Tentu.</font>

83
00:07:05,771 --> 00:07:07,740
<font color=#FFFF00>Kerja bagus.
/ Selamat tinggal.</font>

84
00:07:10,671 --> 00:07:13,440
<font color=#FFFF00>Kenapa kau belum ganti pakaian?
Kau tidak akan pulang?</font>

85
00:07:15,440 --> 00:07:16,641
<font color=#FFFF00>Kalian bisa pergi lebih dulu.</font>

86
00:07:17,750 --> 00:07:20,450
<font color=#FFFF00>Dokter Song dan aku masih ada
sesuatu yang harus dilakukan.</font>

87
00:07:21,281 --> 00:07:24,690
<font color=#FFFF00>Menurutku kalian bisa melakukan
itu lagi di asrama.</font>

88
00:07:24,891 --> 00:07:26,490
<font color=#FFFF00>Kubilang duluan saja.</font>

89
00:07:26,750 --> 00:07:29,461
<font color=#FFFF00>Jika aku boleh mengingatkan
kalian berdua...,</font>

90
00:07:29,791 --> 00:07:33,930
<font color=#FFFF00>...kalian berdua bertanggung jawab
atas makan malam ini.</font>

91
00:07:34,130 --> 00:07:36,531
<font color=#FFFF00>Iya. Apa yang kami makan
jika kalian di sini?</font>

92
00:07:36,531 --> 00:07:38,331
<font color=#FFFF00>Pikirkan sendiri.</font>

93
00:07:38,901 --> 00:07:40,130
<font color=#FFFF00>Atau kelaparan.</font>

94
00:07:40,740 --> 00:07:42,300
<font color=#FFFF00>Tidak makan satu kali
tidak akan membuat kalian mati.</font>

95
00:07:42,740 --> 00:07:44,271
<font color=#FFFF00>Mari kita pergi, Pak Chu.</font>

96
00:07:44,271 --> 00:07:46,110
<font color=#FFFF00>Kita belum selesai bicara.</font>

97
00:07:46,940 --> 00:07:49,281
<font color=#FFFF00>Pak Chu.
/ Kau mendengarku.</font>

98
00:07:51,351 --> 00:07:53,921
<font color=#FFFF00>Kenapa kau tidak mau dengar?</font>

99
00:07:58,921 --> 00:07:59,950
<font color=#FFFF00>Hyun.</font>

100
00:08:00,221 --> 00:08:02,721
<font color=#FFFF00>Kalian ketahuan?
/ Apa maksudmu?</font>

101
00:08:02,721 --> 00:08:05,391
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia memergoki kau dan Dokter Song
menjadi tidak baik?</font>

102
00:08:05,791 --> 00:08:06,791
<font color=#FFFF00>Hei.</font>

103
00:08:07,560 --> 00:08:08,601
<font color=#FFFF00>Lantas...,</font>

104
00:08:08,930 --> 00:08:11,271
<font color=#FFFF00>...menurutmu kenapa mereka
sangat serius begitu?</font>

105
00:08:25,081 --> 00:08:26,510
<font color=#FFFF00>Ini osteosarcoma, kan?</font>

106
00:08:26,510 --> 00:08:29,351
<font color=#FFFF00><i>(Osteosarcoma: Pertumbuhan tulang
yang berbahaya)</i></font>

107
00:08:29,450 --> 00:08:32,690
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau harus melakukan biopsi
untuk memastikannya.</font>

108
00:08:36,560 --> 00:08:38,960
<font color=#FFFF00>Bangun. Ikut denganku.</font>

109
00:08:39,631 --> 00:08:42,230
<font color=#FFFF00>Mari kita segera lakukan biopsi.</font>

110
00:08:44,600 --> 00:08:46,830
<font color=#FFFF00>Lekas ganti pakaian.</font>

111
00:08:47,271 --> 00:08:50,641
<font color=#FFFF00>Pak Chu.
/ Atau pergi saja seperti itu.</font>

112
00:08:51,741 --> 00:08:52,741
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku akan...</font>

113
00:08:54,411 --> 00:08:55,411
<font color=#FFFF00>...menghadapinya.</font>

114
00:08:58,310 --> 00:08:59,611
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa maksudmu?</font>

115
00:09:01,450 --> 00:09:02,881
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku tidak ingin...</font>

116
00:09:04,090 --> 00:09:05,190
<font color=#FFFF00>...orang lain...</font>

117
00:09:06,151 --> 00:09:08,161
<font color=#FFFF00>...tahu kalau aku sakit.</font>

118
00:09:09,361 --> 00:09:10,361
<font color=#FFFF00>Kenapa?</font>

119
00:09:11,391 --> 00:09:12,891
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau takut menjadi gangguan?</font>

120
00:09:13,730 --> 00:09:15,901
<font color=#FFFF00>Siapa peduli? Kita keluarga.</font>

121
00:09:16,161 --> 00:09:19,001
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku tidak meminta bantuan
sebagai kolega.</font>

122
00:09:24,111 --> 00:09:25,771
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku tidak meminta
sebagai Dokter Song.</font>

123
00:09:27,111 --> 00:09:28,611
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku hanya seorang pasien...</font>

124
00:09:29,111 --> 00:09:31,550
<font color=#FFFF00>...yang meminta ahli medis...</font>

125
00:09:32,350 --> 00:09:35,550
<font color=#FFFF00>...untuk merahasiakan
catatan medisnya.</font>

126
00:09:42,391 --> 00:09:43,391
<font color=#FFFF00>Tolong...</font>

127
00:09:45,060 --> 00:09:47,700
<font color=#FFFF00>...jaga rahasiaku, Pak Chu.</font>

128
00:09:56,800 --> 00:09:57,810
<font color=#FFFF00>Baiklah.</font>

129
00:09:58,411 --> 00:10:01,810
<font color=#FFFF00>Bagaimana dengan biopsi?
/ Aku akan menyelesaikannya.</font>

130
00:10:02,411 --> 00:10:03,440
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau yakin?</font>

131
00:10:21,960 --> 00:10:24,401
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Ada gundukan di sini?</i></font>

132
00:10:34,440 --> 00:10:36,611
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Dokter, kau terluka?</i></font>

133
00:11:05,641 --> 00:11:06,940
<font color=#FFFF00>Ini cukup dingin.</font>

134
00:11:07,080 --> 00:11:09,940
<font color=#FFFF00>Hei, hei, apa yang kau lakukan?</font>

135
00:11:09,940 --> 00:11:11,310
<font color=#FFFF00>Hentikan.
/ Kemari.</font>

136
00:11:11,310 --> 00:11:13,050
<font color=#FFFF00>Kemari.
/ Astaga.</font>

137
00:11:14,121 --> 00:11:15,621
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa yang sudah kau lakukan?</font>

138
00:11:15,621 --> 00:11:17,590
<font color=#FFFF00>Sepertinya tukang pos
hanya melemparkannya.</font>

139
00:11:17,590 --> 00:11:20,921
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau kenapa? Kenapa kau selalu
makan kertas?</font>

140
00:11:20,921 --> 00:11:22,460
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau pasti bukan anjing.
Kau kambing, kan?</font>

141
00:11:22,460 --> 00:11:23,891
<font color=#FFFF00>Siapa itu?
/ Siapa apanya?</font>

142
00:11:23,891 --> 00:11:25,891
<font color=#FFFF00>Surat siapa yang dia kunyah?</font>

143
00:11:25,891 --> 00:11:29,730
<font color=#FFFF00>Hanya dia yang tahu.
Namanya ada di perutnya.</font>

144
00:11:30,131 --> 00:11:32,131
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia makan alamatnya?
/ Iya.</font>

145
00:11:39,271 --> 00:11:41,041
<font color=#FFFF00>Milik siapa itu?
/ Aku tidak tahu.</font>

146
00:11:43,111 --> 00:11:44,781
<font color=#FFFF00>"Rumah sakit Royal London"?</font>

147
00:11:45,480 --> 00:11:46,810
<font color=#FFFF00>Ini pasti dari Inggris.</font>

148
00:11:49,850 --> 00:11:51,151
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa untuk Dokter Song?</font>

149
00:11:51,891 --> 00:11:52,891
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa itu?</font>

150
00:11:54,291 --> 00:11:56,320
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa ini?
/ Apa Dokter Song...</font>

151
00:11:56,560 --> 00:11:59,291
<font color=#FFFF00>...mendaftar ke rumah sakit darurat
di Inggris?</font>

152
00:11:59,631 --> 00:12:01,800
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa?
/ Sepertinya begitu.</font>

153
00:12:06,070 --> 00:12:07,100
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau tidak tahu?</font>

154
00:12:07,200 --> 00:12:09,340
<font color=#FFFF00>Ini dia.
/ Apa?</font>

155
00:12:09,340 --> 00:12:11,271
<font color=#FFFF00>Alasan Pak Chu marah.</font>

156
00:12:11,570 --> 00:12:14,041
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia marah karena dokter Song
ingin pergi saat...</font>

157
00:12:14,411 --> 00:12:16,611
<font color=#FFFF00>...kita bisa melakukan operasi
di kapal.</font>

158
00:12:16,781 --> 00:12:17,850
<font color=#FFFF00>Itu masuk akal.</font>

159
00:12:23,651 --> 00:12:24,921
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Kelihatannya sangat enak.</i></font>

160
00:12:29,560 --> 00:12:30,891
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Babi memang yang terbaik.</i></font>

161
00:16:43,440 --> 00:16:45,781
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau bekerja keras sampai larut.</font>

162
00:16:46,350 --> 00:16:47,521
<font color=#FFFF00>Ada apa kau kemari?</font>

163
00:16:47,521 --> 00:16:49,820
<font color=#FFFF00>Pasien menunjukkan tanda-tanda
osteosarcoma.</font>

164
00:16:50,151 --> 00:16:52,090
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku ingin meminta biopsi.</font>

165
00:16:52,621 --> 00:16:55,590
<font color=#FFFF00>"Pasien X"? Nama macam apa ini?</font>

166
00:16:55,590 --> 00:16:57,661
<font color=#FFFF00>Ini calon percobaan klinis.</font>

167
00:16:57,661 --> 00:16:59,391
<font color=#FFFF00>Pasien meminta tanpa nama.</font>

168
00:16:59,391 --> 00:17:01,501
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku mengerti. Baiklah.</font>

169
00:17:01,501 --> 00:17:03,830
<font color=#FFFF00>Berapa lama kira-kira?
/ Mungkin satu hari.</font>

170
00:17:04,301 --> 00:17:06,200
<font color=#FFFF00>Itu bisa lebih cepat jika
kau sedang terburu-buru.</font>

171
00:17:06,200 --> 00:17:09,240
<font color=#FFFF00>Besok pagi?
/ Akan aku usahakan.</font>

172
00:17:09,341 --> 00:17:10,710
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku akan membelikanmu kopi.</font>

173
00:18:01,421 --> 00:18:03,861
<font color=#FFFF00><i>(Kwak Hyun)</i></font>

174
00:18:20,841 --> 00:18:22,940
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Hasil tesnya sudah keluar.</i></font>

175
00:18:22,940 --> 00:18:25,151
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Itu osteosarcoma sesuai dugaanmu.</i></font>

176
00:18:25,811 --> 00:18:29,551
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Itu salah satu jenis kanker
yang paling mematikan.</i></font>

177
00:18:29,651 --> 00:18:32,121
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Jika sudah menyebar ke paru-paru...,</i></font>

178
00:18:32,121 --> 00:18:34,490
<font color=#FFFF00><i>...tingkat bertahan hidup
pasien turun setengahnya.</i></font>

179
00:18:35,520 --> 00:18:38,891
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Aku sudah memberimu hasilnya
jauh lebih awal.</i></font>

180
00:18:38,891 --> 00:18:42,631
<font color=#FFFF00></i>Kau tidak berterimakasih?
Kau sebaiknya membelikan aku kopi.</i></font>

181
00:19:02,020 --> 00:19:03,250
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau darimana?</font>

182
00:19:04,121 --> 00:19:06,520
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku dari UGD.
/ Kau dapat telepon?</font>

183
00:19:08,321 --> 00:19:09,990
<font color=#FFFF00>Kenapa tidak menjawab teleponnya?</font>

184
